    "difficulty": "Intermediate",
    "whatItDoes": "A guide for building MCP (Model Context Protocol) servers that let LLMs interact with external APIs and services. Covers Python (FastMCP), TypeScript (MCP SDK), and C#/.NET (Microsoft MCP SDK), with detailed phases for research, implementation, testing, and evaluation. Also maps the existing Microsoft MCP ecosystem so you know when to build custom vs. reuse.",
