    "whatItDoes": "Azure AI Document Intelligence SDK for .NET wraps the Document Intelligence REST API into a typed client. It extracts text, tables, key-value pairs, and structured fields from PDFs and images using prebuilt models for invoices, receipts, IDs, and tax forms, or custom models you train on your own documents.",
