    "whatItDoes": "Azure.AI.OpenAI is the official .NET client library for Azure OpenAI Service. It provides access to GPT-4, embeddings, DALL-E, and Whisper through a typed C# API. Supports both Azure-hosted deployments and direct OpenAI compatibility.",
