    "whatItDoes": "Azure.ResourceManager.ApiCenter is the .NET SDK for Azure API Center, a service that maintains a centralized inventory of your organization's APIs. It covers the full resource hierarchy: services, workspaces, APIs, versions, specifications, environments, deployments, and custom metadata schemas.",
