    "whatItDoes": "Azure.ResourceManager.MongoDBAtlas is a .NET SDK for managing MongoDB Atlas organizations as Azure ARM resources through the Azure Marketplace integration. It handles the Azure-side lifecycle of Atlas organizations, including creation, updates, tagging, and deletion with unified billing. For cluster and database management, you still use the MongoDB Atlas API directly.",
