    "whatItDoes": "Azure.ResourceManager.Fabric is the .NET SDK for managing Microsoft Fabric capacity resources through Azure Resource Manager. It covers provisioning, scaling, suspending, and resuming Fabric capacities. It does not handle data plane operations like workspaces or lakehouses.",
