    "whatItDoes": "Azure Resource Manager SDK for managing Arize AI Observability and Evaluation organizations in .NET applications. It wraps the ARM API for the ArizeAi.ObservabilityEval resource type, covering create, read, update, and delete operations via Azure Marketplace.",
