    "whatItDoes": "Azure AI Document Intelligence (Form Recognizer) SDK for Java lets you extract structured data from documents using prebuilt models for receipts, invoices, IDs, and tax forms, or custom models you train on your own data. It handles layout extraction, key-value pairs, tables, and document classification.",
