    "whatItDoes": "Legacy Java SDK for Azure Communication Services call management, now deprecated in favor of azure-communication-callautomation. Covers the original CallingServerClient API surface including call recording, participant management, and server call operations. Only relevant when maintaining existing code built on the beta releases.",
