    "whatItDoes": "Azure.Security.KeyVault.Keys is the .NET client library for creating and managing cryptographic keys in Azure Key Vault and Managed HSM. It provides two main clients: KeyClient for key lifecycle operations and CryptographyClient for encrypt, decrypt, sign, verify, wrap, and unwrap operations.",
