    "whatItDoes": "Java client library for Azure Batch, a managed service that runs large-scale parallel and HPC workloads. Lets you create and manage pools of compute nodes, submit jobs, and track tasks through their lifecycle. Supports both sync and async clients, autoscaling, and long-running operations via pollers.",
