    "whatItDoes": "Java SDK for querying Azure Monitor data. Supports Kusto queries against Log Analytics workspaces and fetching metrics from Azure resources using LogsQueryClient and MetricsQueryClient. Note: this package is deprecated; migrate to azure-monitor-query-logs and azure-monitor-query-metrics.",
