    "whatItDoes": "Java SDK for managing cryptographic keys in Azure Key Vault and Managed HSM. Supports RSA, EC, and symmetric key types with HSM backing options. Handles the full key lifecycle including creation, rotation, backup, and deletion, plus cryptographic operations like encrypt, decrypt, sign, verify, and key wrapping.",
