    "whatItDoes": "Python SDK for building AI applications on Microsoft Azure Foundry. Wraps agent creation, thread management, evaluations, connections, deployments, datasets, and indexes under a single `AIProjectClient`. Also provides an OpenAI-compatible client for projects that use standard OpenAI API patterns.",
