    "difficulty": "Intermediate",
    "whatItDoes": "Azure App Configuration SDK for Python provides a client for reading and writing key-value settings, feature flags, and labeled configurations stored in Azure App Configuration. It supports filtering by key prefix or label, creating point-in-time snapshots, and locking settings to prevent changes.",
